  <title>Turkey Burgers</title>
  <filename>turkey_burgers.xml</filename>
  <htmlFilename>turkey_burgers.html</htmlFilename>
  <thumbnail>turkey_burgers.jpeg</thumbnail>
  <category>Dinner</category>
  <category>Lunch</category>
  <diet>FODMAP</diet>
  <diet>EggFree</diet>
  <diet>DiaryFree</diet>
  <ingredient>500 gms turkey mince</ingredient>
  <ingredient>2 spring onions chopped</ingredient>
  <ingredient>2 garlic cloves chopped</ingredient>
  <ingredient>1 medium zucchini grated</ingredient>
  <ingredient>2 tbsp olive oil</ingredient>
  <ingredient>1-2 inches grated ginger</ingredient>
  <ingredient>1 lemon grass finely chopped</ingredient>
  <ingredient>Salt and Pepper to taste</ingredient>
  <step>Mix all ingredients together in a large bowl and make into patties.</step>
  <step>Cook in a couple of tablespoons of olive oil until cooked through and nicely browned.</step>
  <step>Serve with fresh salad and homemade chutney or sauce.</step>
  <step>You can double this recipe.</step>
</recipe>
